      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When Phase B's matcher lands on an AU store that ISN'T an installed Shopfront merchant (target_shop_id=NULL),\nthe hit becomes inbound inventory for #385. Outreach pitch: 'we detected fake-yourstore.shop being issued an\nSSL cert at 14:23 AEST today \u2014 here's the takedown template + claim your Verified badge'. Manual-send only in v1.",
      "originalText": "When Phase B's matcher lands on an AU store that ISN'T an installed Shopfront merchant (target_shop_id=NULL),\nthe hit becomes inbound inventory for #385. Outreach pitch: 'we detected fake-yourstore.shop being issued an\nSSL cert at 14:23 AEST today \u2014 here's the takedown template + claim your Verified badge'. Manual-send only in v1.",
